OL,6,FITV News Investigations Editor Daniel
OL,7,FHewitt discusses Post Office Chairman
OL,8,FNigel Railton's appearance before the
OL,9,FBusiness and Trade Committee
OL,11,FInvestigators who helped wrongly
OL,12,Fprosecute hundreds of sub-postmasters
OL,13,Fshould not still be working for the
OL,14,FPost Office, according to the
OL,15,Forganisation's chairman.
OL,17,FNigel Railton made the comments before
OL,18,Fa session of the Business and Trade
OL,19,FCommittee on Tuesday.
