OL,3,CPost Office Chairman says staff who
OL,4,Chelped prosecute postmasters should go
OL,6,FAsked by the committee's chair, Liam
OL,7,FByrne, as to whether the Post Office
OL,8,Fcan drive through "cultural change" if
OL,9,Fit continues to employ such
OL,10,Finvestigators, Mr Railton said: "No."
OL,12,F"Am I doing something about it? Yes,"
OL,13,FMr Railton added.
OL,15,FMr Railton's comments comes after ITV
OL,16,FNews learned that detectives
OL,17,Finvestigating the Horizion IT scandal
OL,18,Fhad been made aware of at least two
OL,19,Fcases of potential criminal activity
OL,20,Fby Post Office employees.
