OL,4,Chelped prosecute postmasters should go
OL,6,FIt is not known who, or what, the
OL,7,Freferrals relate to.
OL,9,FThe Post Office set up an internal
OL,10,Fprobe, called Project Phoenix, in 2023
OL,11,Fto review allegations made by sub-
OL,12,Fpostmasters about the conduct of Post
OL,13,FOffice investigators who handled their
OL,14,Fcases.
OL,16,FMr Railton, during Tuesday's hearing,
OL,17,Fwas also asked for his thoughts on the
OL,18,Fcost of Project Phoenix.
