OL,10,FMr Byrne said: "Project Phoenix you'll
OL,11,Fhave seen in the news, I think the
OL,12,Fnews was reporting that it cost about
OL,13,F#880,000 in cost of the Post Office
OL,14,Finvestigating sub-postmater complaints
OL,15,Fagainst investigators. Was that a good
OL,16,Fuse of Post Office money, that
OL,17,F#880,000?"
OL,19,F"I haven't got the details, but that's
OL,20,Fan awful amount of money to spend on
OL,21,Fan investigation," Mr Railton replied.
