OL,3,CPost Office Chairman says staff who
OL,4,Chelped prosecute postmasters should go
OL,6,FAt the height of the Horizon scandal,
OL,7,Fsub-postmasters accused by the Post
OL,8,FOffice of theft were subject to police-
OL,9,Fstyle interviews carried out by its
OL,10,Fown internal investigators working for
OL,11,Fits security team.
OL,13,FInterviews and reports carried out by
OL,14,Fthese internal investigators were then
OL,15,Fused as evidence to help convict sub-
OL,16,Fpostmasters.
