OL,3,CPost Office Chairman says staff who
OL,4,Chelped prosecute postmasters should go
OL,6,FDozens of sub-postmasters have made
OL,7,Fcomplaints about the conduct of the
OL,8,Finvestigators the Post Office sent to
OL,9,Finterview them, accusing them of
OL,10,Fbullying, intimidation and omitting
OL,11,Fevidence from their interviews
OL,12,Fregarding faults with the Horizon IT
OL,13,Fsystem, which were ultimately to blame
OL,14,Ffor money going missing.
OL,16,FMore than 900 sub-postmasters were
OL,17,Fprosecuted between 1999 and 2015 after
OL,18,Ffaulty Horizon accounting software
OL,19,Fmade it look as though money was
OL,20,Fmissing from their accounts.
